name: PHP Dorset User Group
tagline: Next meetup Monday, 6 January 2014 from 18:00 to 20:30 (GMT) @ The Libertine, Bournemouth, United Kingdom
body: ### Welcome to PHP Dorset user group So, we're here and started up in November 2013. We've had our first successful meetup on December 2nd 2013! Follow us on twitter and join us on IRC for updates. If you're interested in speaking then please get in touch:- IRC: #phpdorset on freenode.net Twitter: https://twitter.com/phpdorset IRC: [irc://irc.freenode.net:6667/phpdorset](#phpdorset on freenode.net) Events: http://www.eventbrite.co.uk/org/5284449005 Mailing List/Google Group: https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups#!forum/phpdorset Forum: https://moot.it/phpdorset
